---
description: Shared coding standards for frontend and backend
globs:
  - "backend/**/*.py"
  - "frontend/src/**/*.ts"
  - "frontend/src/**/*.tsx"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use clear names and cohesive files.
- Prefer composition over duplication.
- Remove unused code and imports.
- Follow project formatter and linter settings.
- Keep data models, business logic, and transport layers separate.
